---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | AWS Exam Prep"
  description="Privacy policy for the AWS certification practice site."
>
  <section class="surface">
    <div class="eyebrow">Policy</div>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted">
      We collect minimal data to keep this practice site running. No account is required.
      If ads are enabled (e.g., Google AdSense), they may use cookies or similar technologies
      to serve and personalize ads.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Anonymous usage data (page views, browser type) for analytics and performance tuning.</li>
      <li>No user-submitted content is stored; question attempts stay on your device.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Functional cookies may be used for preferences.</li>
      <li>Advertising cookies (if ads are enabled) are managed by the ad network (e.g., Google AdSense).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Analytics and advertising partners may process data per their own policies.</li>
      <li>External fonts or scripts (e.g., Google Fonts) may receive standard request metadata.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Exam Integrity</h2>
    <p>We do not collect or host live/recalled AWS exam questions. This site is for practice and concept reinforcement only.</p>

    <h2>Your Choices</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Use browser controls to clear or block cookies.</li>
      <li>If you have questions or requests, contact us via the Contact page.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy; the latest version will always be posted here.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
